Write a program to calculate the amount of tip you should pay! In European countries, when
A person goes to a restaurant to eat; If the bill is between 50 and 300 euros; Level
Gratuity will be equal to 15% of the invoice amount; Otherwise, the tip amount is 20
A percentage of the amount is billed.
Your duties:
  1) Calculate the tip amount based on the bill. Note that for this permission to use
You don't have if and else commands.
  2) Print the amount of the bill, tip and final payment (bill + tip).
Test data:
Test data 275:1
Test data 40:2
Test data 430:3